@DATABASE "Savage Part 1"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - S - Savage Part 1"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - S
                   ====================================

                               Savage Part 1
                               =============



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(39319,0) zxampoke(57520,0) zxampoke(58601,0)"}         39319,0:57520,0:58601,0
@{"Infinite Energy" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(37557,0) zxampoke(39297,0) zxampoke(58584,0)"}         39319,0:57520,0:58601,0
@{"Lives = x      " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(37299,99)"}         37299,x (x= 1-99)


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
